03:40.910 --> 03:41.630
tetap perlu beri saya

03:41.630 --> 03:42.840
sepasang penyepit.

03:43.430 --> 03:44.560
Betul tak, Pak Tang?

03:45.360 --> 03:45.890
Xiaolan,

03:46.000 --> 03:48.400
